Package: SPLANG
Type: Package
Title: A synthetic Poisson-lognormal-based abundance and network generative model for microbial interaction inference algorithms
Description: 
  A generative model to generate synthetic pairs of underlying taxa interaction
  network and observed abundance data to develop and benchmark microbial interaction
  inference algorithms.
